org.togglz.core.util

Class NamedFeature

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.togglz.core.util.NamedFeature
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Feature

    public class NamedFeature
extends Object
implements Feature
    This class can be used if just the name of a feature is known but not the enum type. It is similar to UntypedFeature but doesn't try to lazily resolve the type when calling name().
    Author:
    Christian Kaltepoth
